LAGOS – Health challenges in a stressful marriage, coping strategies for couples and contemporary issues in marriage are some of the issues that would be discussed at “The Wife” Couples Forum which comes up on Saturday 16th July 2022. The annual event would come under the theme, “Marriage in our contemporary world” and will take place at the Golden Gate Ikoyi, Lagos. A statement signed and made available to Independent Newspaper by ‘The Wife’ Chairperson Dr. (Mrs.) Nkem Okoro explained that the theme was ideal considering the challenges faced by couples in society. Dr. Okoro said that her organisation which was established over 16 years ago aimed to build an excellent home to transform society. The organisation, she said also hoped to empower wives to achieve their God-given purpose in their relationship in all spheres of life as well as achieve a fun-filled marriage and sustain the exciting love between husband and wife.